1. Juče sam *smislila* novi način da organizujemo timski rad. (Yesterday I came up with a new way to organize teamwork.)
2. Molim vas da *smislite* originalan naziv za našu novu kampanju. (Please come up with an original name for our new campaign.)
3. Nisam sigurna kako da *smislim* dobar poklon za njegov rođendan. (I'm not sure how to come up with a good gift for his birthday.)
4. On je jako kreativan i uvek uspeva da *smisli* nešto novo. (He is very creative and always manages to come up with something new.)
5. Da li si *smislio* neki plan za vikend? (Have you thought of any plans for the weekend?)
6. Kada su *smislili* novu tehnologiju za prenos podataka, nisu ni slutili koliki će uticaj imati na društvo. (When they invented the new data transmission technology, they had no idea of the impact it would have on society.)
7. On je veoma lukav i uvek *smišlja* nove načine da izbegne obaveze. (He is very cunning and always devises new ways to avoid responsibilities.)
8. Moramo *smisliti* neki način da smanjimo troškove proizvodnje. (We need to come up with a way to reduce production costs.)
9. Njegova priča se nije *smislila*, sve se zaista dogodilo. (His story wasn't made up, it really happened.)
10. Nema smisla *smišljati* izgovore, jednostavno reci istinu. (There's no point in making up excuses, just tell the truth.)